161
00:16:50,623 --> 00:16:52,420
- ¿Estás bien?
- No sé.

162
00:16:52,458 --> 00:16:53,925
Vamos.

163
00:16:56,545 --> 00:16:58,979
No sé, Lisa.

164
00:16:59,548 --> 00:17:00,947
